exercises.title: Push Up Jacks
exercises.instructions: Perform a push-up, then jump your feet out to the sides and back in, similar to a jumping jack.

exercises.title: Glute Bridge
exercises.instructions: Lie on your back with knees bent, feet flat on the floor. Lift hips toward the ceiling, squeezing glutes at the top.

exercises.title: Reverse Ab Push Up
exercises.instructions: Start in a plank position, then lower your hips toward the floor while keeping your upper body stable.

exercises.title: Wheel Pose
exercises.instructions: Start on your back, bend knees with feet flat on floor, place hands by ears with fingers pointing toward shoulders, then push up to form an arch.

exercises.title: Plank to Squat Jumps
exercises.instructions: Begin in plank position, jump feet forward toward hands, then explosively jump up before returning to plank.

exercises.title: Donkey Kicks
exercises.instructions: On hands and knees, kick one leg back and up while keeping knee bent, focusing on using glute muscles.

exercises.title: Side Turning Kicks
exercises.instructions: From standing position, lift knee up and then extend leg out to the side in a controlled kicking motion.

exercises.title: Raised Feet Wall Plank
exercises.instructions: Place feet on wall while in plank position, increasing the challenge to your core and shoulders.

exercises.title: Side Leg Raises
exercises.instructions: Lie on your side and lift top leg up and down, targeting outer thigh and hip muscles.

exercises.title: Calf Raise with Knee Raise
exercises.instructions: Rise onto toes, then lift one knee toward chest, challenging balance and working calves.

exercises.title: Glute Raises
exercises.instructions: Similar to glute bridges but with extended legs for increased difficulty.

exercises.title: Burpees
exercises.instructions: Full body exercise combining squat, plank, push-up, and jump.

exercises.title: Mountain Climbers
exercises.instructions: In plank position, alternate bringing knees toward chest in a running motion.

exercises.title: Jumping Lunges
exercises.instructions: Alternating lunges with an explosive jump between transitions.

exercises.title: Superman Hold
exercises.instructions: Lie face down and simultaneously raise arms, chest, and legs off the ground.

exercises.instructions: Single-leg squats that require balance, flexibility, and strength.

exercises.instructions: Using a chair or bench, lower body by bending elbows and then push back up.

exercises.instructions: Lie on back, arms extended overhead, legs straight, lift shoulders and legs off floor.

exercises.title: Flutter Kicks

exercises.title: L-Sits
exercises.instructions: Support yourself on hands with legs extended straight in front of you parallel to the ground

exercises.title: Plyo Push-Ups

exercises.title: Scorpion Push-Ups
